text: State Route 303 (SR 303) is a short state highway in Rhea County, Tennessee. For the majority of its length, it is known as Cranmore Cove Road. ==Route description== SR 303 begins in Graysville at an intersection with US 27/SR 29. It goes north through downtown as Dayton Avenue before turning onto Cranmore Cove Road. The highway then goes northeast through a narrow valley between two ridges before coming to an end at an intersection with SR 30 just west of Dayton. The entire route of SR 303 is a two-lane highway. ==Major intersections== ==References== 303 Category:Transportation in Rhea County, Tennessee
title: Tennessee State Route 303
